          </span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Why Choose the <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Swiss Alps</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            The Swiss Alps represent the pinnacle of luxury relocation, offering unmatched lifestyle quality, favorable tax arrangements, and absolute discretion.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Iconic Alpine Resorts</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              St. Moritz, Gstaad, Zermatt, Andermatt, Crans-Montana, Verbier — world-renowned destinations for luxury living.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 9V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm7-5a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">HNWI Relocation & Lump-Sum Taxation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Pauschalbesteuerung (lump-sum taxation) available for high-net-worth individuals. Negotiate favorable tax deals with cantons.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 3 -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Year-Round Lifestyle</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              World-class skiing, hiking, luxury shopping, Michelin dining, cultural events — the Alps offer four-season elegance.
